    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        I'm the Co-Founder & ML Engineer at <strong>Singularity Forge</strong>, building AI-powered SaaS products
        and leading R&D in satellite/drone technology for environmental mapping. Before this, I worked as an
        AI Engineer at <strong>Omega Labs</strong> on any-to-any multimodal models, and spent 3 years as a
        Senior AI Engineer at <strong>Samsung Research & Development</strong> shipping computer vision models
        to flagship Galaxy devices.
      </p>

      <p>
        My research background includes work at <strong>KAUST</strong> (3D COMPaT, published at <strong>ECCV 2022 Oral</strong>),
        <strong>UC San Diego</strong> (3D shape reconstruction with Prof. Hao Su), and the
        <strong>Indian Institute of Science</strong> (unsupervised LiDAR reconstruction).
      </p>

      <p>
